data.description: Enjoy golf course living in this patio home overlooking the 9th Fairway of the Point course at the Golf Club of Atascocita! Soaring ceiling in the den and plenty of windows to enjoy the views. Primary bedroom and bath with updated shower are located on the 1st floor.  Secondary bedrooms and bath are upstairs. Study with French doors is located off the entry with the kitchen and dining area on the other side of entry.  Kitchen has updated appliances, ample counter space for meal prep, and pantry, too.  Inside laundry room is located off the kitchen. Full 2-car garage with door opener. Huge deck in back to enjoy the outdoors. Home has new carpet and fresh paint, new water heater and new electrical box. Great quiet community of patio homes located in Pinehurst of Atascocita. Close to shopping, schools, dining and an easy commute to downtown!
